<div type="abstract"><head>Offener Brief des Rates</head><p>Der Rat bevollmächtigt Peter Haller und Peter Volckamer zur Vertretung bei dem von Viztum und Räten Herzog Johanns III. von Straubing-Holland angesetzten Gerichtstag gegen Weinmar Ecker am Samstag vor Bartholomäustag in Straubing.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_210" id="105r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"/>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_210_r1l18">VVır dıe <expan>Burge<ex>r</ex></expan> etc . Bekennen etc Von <expan>ſölıch<ex>er</ex></expan> ſprüche <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> dıe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_210_r1l19">VVeinmar Eker ʒu <expan>Saldemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> ʒu vns maint ʒu <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> . <expan>Daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ein </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_210_r1l20">tag <expan>ʒwıſch<ex>en</ex></expan> ſein vnd <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> berett ıſt gen Strawbıng . für vnſers </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_210_r1l21"><expan>gnedıg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>cʒog</expan> <expan>Johanſ<ex>en</ex></expan> vıcʒtum vnd dıe Rete in <expan>Nıd<ex>er</ex>n</expan> payern </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_210_r1l22">auf den ſamſtag am achttentag vor ſand Barthlomeus tag </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_210_r1l23">ſchıerıſt Daʒ wır <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> lıeben <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> vnd <expan>Ratgeſell<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . <expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_210_r1l24">Haller dem <expan>elt<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vnd <expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan> volkmeırn <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>voll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd <expan>gancʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_210_r1l25">gwalt <expan>gegeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> mıt dıſem <expan>br<ex>ief</ex></expan> / Vns auf dem </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_210_r1l26">tag ʒu <expan>v<ex>er</ex>antwurt<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd auch ʒu <expan>entſchuldıg<ex>en</ex></expan> ob des not beſchıht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_210_r1l27">vnd dıe ſache an <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> ſtat ʒu handeln ʒu tun vnd ʒu laſſen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_210_r1l28">on <expan>geu<ex>er</ex>de</expan> . Mıt <expan>vrk<ex>unde</ex></expan> etc . </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_210_r1l29"><expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ıııȷ<hi rend="sup">a</hi> <expan>vıgı<ex>lia</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_210_r1l30"><expan>aſſu<ex>m</ex>p<ex>ci</ex><hi rend="sup">o<ex>n</ex>ıs</hi></expan> marıe <expan>vırg<ex>in</ex>ıs</expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_210" id="105r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab/></div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Wir, die <expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> etc., bekennen etc. von
                                <expan>sölich<ex>er</ex></expan> sprüche
                            <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, die Weinmar Eker zu
                                <expan>Saldemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> zu uns maint zu
                                <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>, <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ein
                        tag <expan>zwisch<ex>en</ex></expan> sein und <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        berett ist gen Strawbing für unsers <expan>gnedig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren,</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>czog</expan>
<expan>Johans<ex>en,</ex></expan> vicztum und die rete in
                        <expan>Nid<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Payern auf den <app><note><q type="date">samstag am achttentag
                            vor sand Barthlomeus tag schierist</q>17.08.1415</note></app>, daz wir <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> lieben <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> und
                                <expan>ratgesell<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan> Haller dem <expan>elt<ex>er</ex>n</expan> und
                                <expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan> Volkmeirn
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>voll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und <expan>gancze<ex>n</ex></expan> gwalt
                                <expan>gegeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> mit disem
                                <expan>br<ex>ief</ex></expan>, uns auf dem tag zu
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>antwurt<ex>en</ex></expan> und auch zu
                                <expan>entschuldig<ex>en,</ex></expan> ob des not beschiht, und die
                        sache an <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> stat zu handeln, zu tun und zu
                        lassen, on <expan>gev<ex>er</ex>de</expan>. Mit
                            <expan>urk<ex>unde</ex></expan> etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> iiii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>vigi<ex>lia</ex></expan>
<expan>assu<ex>m</ex>p<ex>ci</ex><hi rend="sup">o<ex>n</ex>is</hi></expan>
                        Marie <expan>virg<ex>in</ex>is.</expan>
</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
